name: Flavours Of Malaysia
description: Let us share our passion for Delicious Malaysian Food with You! Simply Enak is a young business providing Food Experiences in the area of Kuala Lumpur Malaysia. We provide food walks in Petaling Street (China Town) as well as tailor-made Food Experiences. Come join us on a Food Experience bringing you to the most authentic places where you will taste the best of what Malaysia's cuisine has to offer!
